                <h1 class="title big">Diarrhea</h1>
                <p style="color:#fff;">Avoid foods that are milk-based, greasy, high-fiber, or very sweet because these are likely to aggravate diarrhea.

                </p>
                
              <a href="#services" class="cs-down"></a>
